utodesk Gallery 2.0          </li> <li>            Bird Watch          </li> <li>            Craigdarroch AR          </li> <li>            Digital Sandbox          </li> <li>            My Ocean World          </li> <li>            Planete MTL          </li> <li>            Wheelhouse and touch screen exhibit          </li> </ul>"},{"location":"blog/tags/#tag:vuforia-sdk","title":"Vuforia SDK","text":"<ul> <li>            Craigdarroch AR          </li> </ul>"},{"location":"blog/tags/#tag:ios","title":"iOS","text":"<ul> <li>            Autodesk Gallery 2.0          </li> <li>            Craigdarroch AR          </li> </ul>"},{"location":"blog/2021/02/01/autodesk-gallery-20/","title":"Autodesk Gallery 2.0","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["iOS","ARKit","Unity3D"]},{"location":"blog/2015/06/01/twitter-enabled-candy-machine/","title":"Twitter enabled candy machine","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["Arduino","Raspberry Pi","Motors","Twitter (X) API"]},{"location":"blog/2015/12/01/cell-phone-disco/","title":"Cell Phone Disco","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>"},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/","title":"Craigdarroch AR","text":"<p>For this project, we created an iOS content delivery system based on indoor location. It also features three different Augmented Reality scenes for different rooms inside the castle.</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#images","title":"Images","text":"<ul> <li> AR 1 </li> <li> AR 2 </li> <li> Ipads </li> <li> Location Aware </li> </ul>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#videos","title":"Videos","text":"Craigdarroch Augmented Reality. Courtesy of NGX Interactive","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#location","title":"Location","text":"<p>Victoria, BC</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#client","title":"Client","text":"<p>Craigdarroch Castle</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#date","title":"Date","text":"<p>May 2016</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#links","title":"Links","text":"<p>https://thecastle.ca</p> <p>https://ngxinteractive.com/project/craigdarroch-castle/</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#technical-environment","title":"Technical Environment","text":"<p>Unity3D, iOS, Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons, Vuforia SDK</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2016/05/01/craigdarroch-ar/#awards","title":"Awards","text":"<p>National Association for Interpretation (NAI) \u2013 Interpretive Media Awards, Digital Media Category, 2nd place. 2017</p>","tags":["Unity3D","iOS","Estimote Bluetooth LE beacons","Vuforia SDK"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/","title":"Exquisite Corpse","text":"<p>For the exquisite corpse, the team decided to create a collaborative space as a creative outlet for the students of our master\u2019s program.</p> <p>This short time-lapse video created with screen captures of the website, shows what we collected during the course of about a week:</p> <p></p> <p>Here\u2019s an extract of the original description that was included in the website:</p> <p>The exquisite corpse is a private shared space for the 54 students of the cdm\u2019s cohort 9. We sought to address the need of artistic forms of social communication. We saw this project as an opportunity to build an elegant and compelling experience.</p> <p>Please visit the blog for more information.</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#videos","title":"Videos","text":"","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#location","title":"Location","text":"<p>Vancouver, BC</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#client","title":"Client","text":"<p>The Centre for Digital Media</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#date","title":"Date","text":"<p>December 2014</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#link","title":"Link","text":"<p>https://artifraction.com/ec/</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2014/12/01/exquisite-corpse/#technical-environment","title":"Technical Environment","text":"<p>Node.js, MongDB, Javascript, HTML</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2015/06/01/graffdrone/","title":"GraffDrone","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["Parrot ARDroneSDK","Javascript","HTML","CSS","Node.js"]},{"location":"blog/2015/02/01/livecity/","title":"LiveCity","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["Node.js","MongDB","Javascript","HTML"]},{"location":"blog/2018/05/01/my-ocean-world/","title":"My Ocean World","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["C++","Unity3D"]},{"location":"blog/2018/04/30/bird-watch/","title":"Bird Watch","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["Unity3D","Arduino"]},{"location":"blog/2017/06/01/planete-mtl/","title":"Planete MTL","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["TouchDesigner","Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Node.js","MongDB"]},{"location":"blog/2016/09/01/quantum-the-exhibition/","title":"Quantum: The Exhibition","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>"},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/","title":"Digital Sandbox","text":"<p>We process the point cloud data from a Kinect V2 in Unity to create the colour gradient that is projected on the sand. This was my first project at NGX Interactive.</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#images","title":"Images","text":"<ul> <li> Drought </li> <li> Flood </li> <li> Flood </li> <li> Normal </li> <li> Installation </li> <li> Prototype </li> </ul>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#videos","title":"Videos","text":"","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#location","title":"Location","text":"<p>Victoria, BC</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#client","title":"Client","text":"<p>Telus World of Science Edmonton</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#date","title":"Date","text":"<p>November 2015</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#link","title":"Link","text":"<p>http://ngxinteractive.com/portfolio/telus-world-of-science-edmonton-digital-sandbox/</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#technical-environment","title":"Technical Environment","text":"<p>Unity3D, Kinect v2</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2015/11/01/digital-sandbox/#awards","title":"Awards","text":"<p>Communicator Awards \u2013 Award of Distinction \u2013 Interactive Multimedia \u2013 Children\u2019s Audience Category, 2016.</p>","tags":["Projection Mapping","Unity3D","Kinect v2"]},{"location":"blog/2017/01/01/scotia-city/","title":"Scotia City","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>"},{"location":"blog/2018/04/01/test-tube-interactive/","title":"Test tube Interactive","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>"},{"location":"blog/2015/04/01/wheelhouse-and-touch-screen-exhibit/","title":"Wheelhouse and touch screen exhibit","text":"<p>This is a draft. Please check back later.</p>","tags":["Unity3D"]},{"location":"blog/archive/2021/","title":"2021","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2018/","title":"2018","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2017/","title":"2017","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2016/","title":"2016","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2015/","title":"2015","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2014/","title":"2014","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/draft/","title":"Draft","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/augmented-reality/","title":"Augmented Reality","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/projection-mapping/","title":"Projection Mapping","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/web/","title":"Web","text":""},{"location":"blog/page/2/","title":"Projects","text":""},{"location":"blog/page/3/","title":"Projects","text":""},{"location":"blog/archive/2015/page/2/","title":"2015","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/draft/page/2/","title":"Draft","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/draft/page/3/","title":"Draft","text":""}]}